lass=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/gal/3?lang=spa&amp;id=p2#p2\">Gálatas 3:2<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jarom/1?lang=spa&amp;id=p4#p4\">Jarom 1:4<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/32?lang=spa&amp;id=p28#p28\">Alma 32:28<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/morm/9?lang=spa&amp;id=p25#p25\">Mormón 9:25<\/a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/ether/4?lang=spa&amp;id=p11#p11\">Éter 4:11<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<\/footer>",
